<% content_for :title, "FAQ & help — Subh Vivaah" %>

<div class="<%= site_page_shell_class %>">
  <%= render "shared/app_header" %>

  <main class="<%= site_page_main_class %>">
    <div class="container">
      <%= render "shared/flash_strip" %>
      <h1 class="<%= site_page_title_class %>">Help &amp; FAQ</h1>
      <p class="<%= site_page_lead_class %>">
        Quick answers about membership, privacy, and using Subh Vivaah.
      </p>
      <div class="<%= site_prose_card_class %>">
        <h2>Is registration free?</h2>
        <p>Yes. You can sign up, create a profile, and explore basic search for free. Paid plans unlock contact details and full messaging as described on <%= link_to "Membership & pricing", pricing_path %>.</p>

        <h2>How do I upgrade?</h2>
        <p>Open <%= link_to "Membership", pricing_path %> and choose a plan. Checkout integration can be connected when you go live; until then, <%= link_to "contact us", contact_path %> for manual upgrades in demo environments.</p>

        <h2>Who can see my phone number?</h2>
        <p>On free membership, contact details are not shown to others. On eligible paid plans, visibility follows your settings and the other member’s plan — we never publish your number on public pages.</p>

        <h2>How do messages and notifications work?</h2>
        <p>
          When someone messages you or views your profile (with deduplication), you will see alerts under
          <% if user_signed_in? %>
            <%= link_to "Notifications", notifications_path %>.
          <% else %>
            Notifications (after you sign in).
          <% end %>
          Interest alerts may be added in a future update.
        </p>

        <h2>How do I report a problem?</h2>
        <p>Use <%= link_to "Feedback & report issue", feedback_path %> or <%= link_to "contact", contact_path %> with details and screenshots if possible.</p>

        <p class="mt-6">
          Still stuck? <%= link_to "Contact support", contact_path %>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%= render "shared/site_footer" %>
</div>
